  OSCARified User File Synchronization System
  GPL
  System Environment/Base

    Jason Brechin
    jbrechin@ncsa.uiuc.edu


  The OSCAR User Synchronization System keeps the users
and groups synchronizaed from the the central OSCAR server out to the
OSCAR compute nodes. Whenever any of the following happens, the users
and groups on the OSCAR server are copied to the OSCAR clients:
periodically (configurable minute).



      ssh-oscar



      sync_users-oscar
